OL,3,CEnd 'unnecessary suffering' caused by
OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap, SNP says
OL,6,FHowever, SNP MP Alison Thewliss said a
OL,7,Fpotentially incoming Labour government
OL,8,Fshould "grow a backbone" and scrap the
OL,9,Fpolicy if the Conservatives do not.
OL,11,FThe policy prevents families from
OL,12,Fclaiming benefits for a third or
OL,13,Fsubsequent children born after April
OL,14,F6, 2017.
OL,16,FAn associated so-called rape clause
OL,17,Fgrants exemptions for a child born as
OL,18,Fa result of "non-consensual
OL,19,Fconception".
